<h1 id=about>About Luke</h1>
<p class=lead>I am a <b>Website Designer</b> and <b>Developer</b> with fresh, new ideas. I am a firm believer that websites should be <b>simple</b> and <b>pure</b>. Users should be able to <b>navigate them with ease</b> and find what they’re looking for in the least amount of clicks possible. </p>
<p class=lead style="font-style: italic;">“Why would a company confuse the very people they need in order to make the business exist in the first place?” </p>
<p class=lead>From start-up companies to existing companies looking to rejuvenate life into their online presence by having the right ideas, productivity can always be boosted.
</p>
